channel.title: Andrew Adams - Bonfire (HYDRANS Remix)
channel.description:
Andrew Adams - Bonfire (HYDRANS Remix) *headphones recommended*
[Click here!](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/andrew-adams-bonfire-hydrans) [or here (my soundcloud)](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans)
My remix of @Andrew_Adams' track Bonfire!
I just want to say thanks to Andrew for letting this happen! Check him out here: [Andrew Adams](https://soundcloud.com/user-andrewadams) Also, the original song is amazing! Check it out here: [Andrew Adams – Bonfire](https://soundcloud.com/user-andrewadams/bonfire)
Let me know how it turned out! Any listens and likes are appreciated as well as feedback!
Thanks! ~ HYDRANS
